# Rasm C# Production

Read `.claude/skills/coding-csharp/SKILL.md`, `CLAUDE.md`, root `AGENTS.md`, and the nearest nested `AGENTS.md`.

## Architecture

- Keep one OOP capsule per native boundary, with FP/ROP internals.
- Prefer `Fin<T>`, `Validation<Error,T>`, `Eff<RT,T>`, `Option`, folds, exhaustive switches, and typed failures.
- Use Thinktecture `[Union]`, `[SmartEnum]`, and value objects to collapse sibling types and switches.
- Convert nullable, bool, disposable, command, document, and host-specific effects at the boundary.

## Do Not Add

- Helper, util, manager, common, options, params, or compatibility-shim files.
- Wrapper-only RhinoCommon, GH2, Eto, LanguageExt, or MathNet renames.
- Domain `try`/`catch`, exception control flow, mutable accumulation, or unbounded primitives where a typed invariant exists.
- `RhinoDoc.ActiveDoc` when a command, UI, or document context already supplies a document.

## Host Baseline

Target RhinoWIP on macOS, GH2, Eto, and app-bundle references from `Directory.Build.props`. Verify risky host APIs with `bash scripts/rhino.sh api doctor|xml|types|decompile`.

## Validation

Run `bash scripts/check-cs.sh check` for coherent C# changes. Run `full` only when trigger build/config files change.
